data.description: Introducing 124 Fernwood Drive, a charming and spacious 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled in the serene outskirts of Harrington, just outside the city limits. This property offers the perfect blend of peaceful country living and convenient access to amenities. Situated on a generous 1-acre lot, this one-level dwelling provides easy and comfortable living for you and your family.  As you step inside, you'll appreciate the modern touches, including, updated flooring,  stainless steel appliances and ceiling fan in the well-appointed kitchen, making meal preparation and entertaining a breeze.   One of the standout features of this home is the lovely deck on the rear, where you can unwind and enjoy the tranquility of your surroundings, perfect for morning coffee or evening relaxation. With its spacious layout, and No HOA restrictions, this property offers plenty of room to explore, play, or even start your own garden or build a barn.  Additionally, this property comes with a valuable bonus – not one, but two sheds that convey with the home. These sheds provide ample storage space for your outdoor equipment, tools, or can be customized to suit your specific needs. With these extra storage options, you'll have plenty of room to keep your belongings organized and secure.  Located just minutes away from Browns Branch Park, you'll have easy access to outdoor recreation, picnicking, and enjoying the natural beauty of the area. Whether you're looking for a peaceful retreat or a place to call home, 124 Fernwood Drive offers the best of both worlds – a quiet, spacious haven with all the modern conveniences you need. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your new home!
